data.description: Welcome to your urban sanctuary! This stunning modern loft in the heart of Midtown has been described as "a vibe" and offers artistic, eclectic style in an unbeatable location. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by polished concrete floors that seamlessly blend the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The soaring 10 ft ceilings and expansive double pane windows sit just within the treetops and above the intersection of Peachtree and 7th offering some of the best people watching and views of parade routes in Midtown. An open concept entertainer's kitchen has been outfitted with brand new Samsung Bespoke appliances and has tons of storage in the oversized pantry. Walking from the bedroom through the laundry and oversized closet, you'll find the recently updated bathroom featuring an expanded walk-in shower and upgraded marble vanity. A rare highlight to this unit is the available second garage parking spot - so hard to find in a one bedroom condo intown! Building amenities include an in-ground pool with outdoor grills, fitness center, dog park, a club room, two covered parking spots and 24-hour concierge service, providing a safe, convenient and enjoyable lifestyle. Located in the center of all of the Midtown action, you'll be steps away from an abundance of restaurants, boutiques, art galleries, coffee shops, gyms and entertainment options such as the Historic Fox Theater. Walk or bike over to the Beltline, Piedmont Park or O4W and Ponce City Market. The options are endless! Public transportation and major highways are just moments away, making your daily commute a breeze. This is the intown lifestyle you've been looking for!
